reviewText: I didn't buy this from Amazon.com, but rented it from Netflix. I'm a huge Kylie fan, and this video is the worst produced schlock I have ever seen. I almost entirely appears in a cartoon tv box ... smaller than the actual tv screen ... and is narrated by extreme close-ups of two people who never reveal who they are ... they are just talking heads. Ridiculous. Absolutely no new information or video here. Stupid stupid stupid. Do NOT waste your money.
